data.description: Mountain Views all around from this 13 acres sitting on a gentle ridge. Open pasture for horses and all your animals. Southern Santa Fe County, only 6 miles to I40 yet a world away. Enjoy open spaces in this rural, quiet neighborhood of well kept homes and county maintained roads. Fenced with new steel fence on 3 sides, up to 75 additional acres available. Close to Estancia Valley Classical Academy, South Mountain Elementary, Wal-Mart and Smith's.
